  {
    's': 3,
    'a': 154,
    't':
        'then after distress he sent down upon you security drowsiness overcoming a faction of you while another faction worried about themselves thinking of allāh other than the truth the thought of ignorance saying is there anything for us in this matter say indeed the matter belongs completely to allāh they conceal within themselves what they will not reveal to you they say if there was anything we could have done in the matter we would not have been killed right here say even if you had been inside your houses those decreed to be killed would have come out to their death beds so that allāh might test what is in your breasts and purify what is in your hearts and allāh is knowing of that within the breasts'
  },
  {
