    't':
        'allāh would not leave the believers in that you are in until he separates the evil from the good nor would allāh reveal to you the unseen but allāh chooses of his messengers whom he wills so believe in allāh and his messengers and if you believe and fear him then for you is a great reward'
  },
  {
